Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Tagaytay, Philippines
Description: A city south of Manila, in a densely forested mountainous region that overlooks Taal Volcano. The lake the volcano resides in is actually a submerged caldera.

Name: Flekaskilin, Thingvellir, Iceland
Description: A geologic and historic wonder in Southwestern Iceland. It is an ancient Nordic political meeting ground, it is a point in the Golden Circle route.

Name: Takaragawa Onsen, Gunma, Japan
Description: An ancient hot springs resort located within a mountainous valley northwest of Tokyo. Built along both sides of flowing rocky stream, legend has it the 12th emperor of Japan was once healed there.

Name: Ogden Point Breakwater, Victoria, BC Canada
Description: A 1.1 mile long breakwater walkway at Victoria Harbour. The lighthouse at the end is an excellent place to view the sunset.

Name: Kaanapali Beach, Hawaii
Description: A beautiful beach located at the most western point of the island Maui, facing the island Lanai.
